'''''Star Wars Insider'' 53''' is the fifty-third issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands in [[April]] [[2001]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk" {{C|by [[Jeff Quick]]}}
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Prequel Update]] with [[Rick McCallum]]" {{C|by [[Dan Madsen]]}}
*"[[Star News]]"
*"[[The Jawa Trader]]"
*"[[Comics Link]]" &mdash; What Was... {{C|by [[David Land|Dave Land]]}}
*"[[Bookshelf]]" &mdash; Keyes to the Galaxy {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Gamescape]]" &mdash; [[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']] {{C|by [[Blake Fischer]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; Is ''Star Wars'' Collecting Dead? {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Dear 2-1B]]"
*"[[The Last Page]]"

===Features===
*"[[Dark Force Rising: An Interview with Ian McDiarmid]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*:<small>When he's bad, he's very bad. [[Ian McDiarmid]] explains why Palpatine's motives are more suspect than ever. [[Scott Chernoff]]'s looking at evil in a whole new light.</small>
*"[[Getting to the Bottom of the Topps Star Wars Trading Cards|Getting to the Bottom of the Topps ''Star Wars'' Trading Cards]]" {{C|by [[Michael G. Ryan]]}}
*:<small>That was a gun? From naughty [[C-3PO/Legends|Threepio]] to autographed chase cards, Topps has put out enough ''Star Wars'' trading cards to make Pikachu jealous. Take a look at the history of Topps ''Star Wars'' trading cards, courtesy of [[Michael G. Ryan]].</small>
*"[[The Essential Guide to Alien Species (real-world book)|''The Essential Guide to Alien Species'']]: Anthropology 101"
*:<small>''Insider'' gives you a sneak peek at the upcoming ''Essential Guide to Aliens'' with extensive data on [[Rodian/Legends|Rodians]], [[Verpine/Legends|Verpine]], and [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. And this is just the preview!</small>

